Type: Package
Package: CondDensReg
Title: Conditional density regression for individual-level data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Alexander", "Fottner", , "alexander.fottner@uni-a.de", role = "aut"),
    person("Eva-Maria", "Maier", , "eva-maria.maier@hu-berlin.de", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Lea", "Runge", , "lea.runge.1@hu-berlin.de", role = "aut")
  )
Maintainer: Eva-Maria Maier <eva-maria.maier@hu-berlin.de>
Description: Structured additive regression models for mixed (discrete/continuous)
    densities as response with scalar covariates, fitted via Poisson regression
    models based on 'mgcv', where the continuous part of the density
    is approximated via histograms. Implementation for Maier et al. (2025b)
    <doi:.../arXiv...>.
License: GPL-2
